# ── Internal ops files — never publish ──
# The Pages deploy workflow uploads the entire repo root (path: .), so anything
# committed under request/ is downloadable at www.rsmd365.com/...  Keep setup
# scripts and internal docs local only (OneDrive still backs them up).
request/SETUP.md
request/provision-lists.ps1
request/request-options.csv

# Runtime secret (flow URLs). Injected at deploy from GitHub Secrets.
# The .example template stays tracked so the shape is documented.
# Centralized at repo root, shared by /request/ and /board/.
config.js
request/config.js

# Belt-and-suspenders: no PowerShell or internal setup docs ever ship
*.ps1
